'''吉爾·都賽佩'''（{{lang|fr|Gilles Duceppe}}，{{IPA-fr|ʒil dysɛp}}；{{bd|1947年|7月22日}}），[[加拿大|加拿大]]政治人物，[[魁北克独立运动|魁北克独立运动]]支持者，并在1996年、1997-2011年以及2015年三段時期担任魁独党派[[魁北克集团|魁北克集团]]的党魁。他曾於1990年-2011年間擔任[[加拿大國會|加拿大國會]][[加拿大國會下議院|下议院]]议员，代表[[魁北克省|魁北克省]]的勞里埃－聖瑪莉選區（{{lang|fr|Laurier—Sainte-Marie}}），期間從1997年3月至6月短暂担任[[加拿大官方反对党领袖|下议院官方反对党领袖]]。魁人政團在[[2011年加拿大國會下議院選舉|2011年聯邦大選]]中大敗，都賽佩亦失掉自己的議席，因此他辞任党魁。四年后他重回魁北克集团擔任黨魁並帶領該黨競逐[[2015年加拿大國會下議院選舉|2015年聯邦大選]]<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/canadavotes2011/story/2011/05/02/cv-election-bloc-wrap-652.html|title = Duceppe quits after BQ crushed in Quebec|publisher = CBC News|accessdate = 3 May 2011|date = 2 May 2011|archive-date = 2013-05-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130520213346/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/canadavotes2011/story/2011/05/02/cv-election-bloc-wrap-652.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://montrealgazette.com/news/quebec/gilles-duceppe-to-reprise-role-as-bloc-quebecois-leader-source|title = "Willingness to be united" pushed Gilles Duceppe to accept Bloc Québécois leadership|publisher = [[蒙特利尔憲報|Montreal Gazette]]|accessdate = 10 June 2015|date = 10 June 2015|archive-date = 2020-12-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201220182233/https://montrealgazette.com/news/quebec/gilles-duceppe-to-reprise-role-as-bloc-quebecois-leader-source|dead-url = no}}</ref>，然而他未能重奪下议院議席並再度辞去黨魁職務<ref>{{Cite web|title = Bloc Québécois Leader Gilles Duceppe to step down|url = http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/montreal/gilles-duceppe-reacts-federal-election-1.3282887|website = www.cbc.ca|accessdate = 2015-10-22|archive-date = 2020-11-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201108140729/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/montreal/gilles-duceppe-reacts-federal-election-1.3282887}}</ref>。

== 早年生活 ==
都賽佩出生于魁北克[[蒙特利尔|蒙特利尔]]<ref name="LOP"/>，母親為埃萊恩·羅利（{{lang|fr|Hélène Rowley}}），父親為演员讓·都賽佩（{{lang|fr|Jean Duceppe}}），外祖父約翰·羅利（{{lang|en|John James Rowley}}）是一个英国人<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XIeelMJSFGM|title = Gilles Duceppe on Quebec Sovereignty|publisher = YouTube|date = 2010-04-08|accessdate = 2011-06-06|archive-date = 2016-04-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160416040850/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XIeelMJSFGM|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="autogenerated1"/>。他父親曾於1954年協助讓·德拉波（{{lang|fr|Jean Drapeau}}）競逐蒙特婁市長，並於1961年成為[[加拿大新民主黨|加拿大新民主黨]]的創始黨員之一<ref name="autogenerated1"/>。

都賽佩在六年级时因为抱怨说英语的学生得到老师的优待后，被英语为母语的老师掌掴；都賽佩称他打回了那位老师一耳光<ref name="autogenerated1"/><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.cbc.ca/news2/canadavotes/leadersparties/leaders-duceppe.html|title = Gilles Duceppe, elegant separatist|year = 2008|work = CBC News|accessdate = 16 April 2014|archive-date = 2017-04-02|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170402001554/http://www.cbc.ca/news2/canadavotes/leadersparties/leaders-duceppe.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。受到由[[瑞內·勒維克|瑞內·勒維克]]創辦的魁北克独立运动组织主權關聯運動（{{lang|fr|Mouvement Souveraineté-Association}}）所啟發，他於20岁成為魁獨支持者<ref name="autogenerated1">{{Cite news|url = http://www.cbc.ca/canadavotes2004/leadersparties/leaders/bio_duceppe.html|title = Gilles Duceppe: Leader, Bloc Québécois|publisher = CBC.ca|accessdate = 2011-05-12|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160310204340/http://www.cbc.ca/canadavotes2004/leadersparties/leaders/bio_duceppe.html|archive-date = 2016-03-10|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

都賽佩在聖路-{易}-山學院（{{lang|fr|Collège Mont-Saint-Louis}}）完成高中教育后到[[蒙特利尔大学|蒙特利尔大学]]攻读政治学，1968年成为魁北克学生联盟（{{lang|fr|Union générale des étudiants du Québec}}）副主席，1970年起担任該校學生報章《拉丁區》（{{lang|fr|''Quartier Latin''}}）的總經理，但没有完成学位。他於1972年成為奧雪來嘉－邁松訥夫（{{lang|fr|Hochelaga-Maisonneuve}}）居民委員會的調停員，曾任醫院夜更护士助理達五年<ref name="autogenerated1"/>，並於1977年成为皇家維多利亞醫院（{{lang|en|Royal Victoria Hospital}}）的职员代表<ref name="CE">{{cite web|url=https://www.thecanadianencyclopedia.ca/en/article/gilles-duceppe|title=Gilles Duceppe|publisher=The Canadian Encyclopedia|first1=Jean|last1=Chartier|first2=Myriam|last2=Fontaine|date=2015-10-22|accessdate=2020-04-18|archive-date=2020-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027041902/https://thecanadianencyclopedia.ca/en/article/gilles-duceppe|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

這些年間他倡議[[共产主义|共产主义]]，并且加入[[毛主義|毛主義]]政党加拿大工人共产党（{{lang|en|Workers' Communist Party of Canada}}），期間因敵對行為而被医院开除<ref name="gm61404">{{Cite news|title = ''The Globe and Mail'' on Duceppe|url = http://web.archive.org/web/20040901171152/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/servlet/ArticleNews/TPStory/LAC/20040614/ELECDUCEPPE14|accessdate = April 22, 2014|newspaper = The Globe and Mail|date = 14 June 2004|archive-date = 2004-09-01|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20040901171152/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/servlet/ArticleNews/TPStory/LAC/20040614/ELECDUCEPPE14}}</ref>。他又於[[1980年魁北克公民投票|1980年魁北克公民投票]]中故意作废选票，并謂魁北克人应集中精力對抗资本主义<ref name="gm61404"/>。他后来称加入該党為一错误抉擇<ref name="autogenerated1"/><ref name="gm61404"/>。他於1981年成为國家職工會聯會（{{lang|fr|Confédération des syndicats nationaux}}）的工會組織员，1986年則成為該機構的谈判员<ref name="gm61404"/>。

== 晉身國會 ==
都賽佩於1990年競逐蒙特婁勞里埃－聖瑪莉選區（{{lang|fr|Laurier—Sainte-Marie}}）的[[加拿大国会下议院|加拿大国会下议院]]議席补选，結果擊敗[[加拿大自由党|加拿大自由党]]候選人葛達理（{{lang|fr|Denis Coderre}}）成功當選，首度晉身國會<ref name="LOP"/>。

在魁北克集团正式獲加拿大選舉局註冊為政黨前，都賽佩以独立议员身份在國會議政。除都賽佩外，所有魁北克集团國會议员皆以[[加拿大进步保守党|加拿大进步保守党]]或加拿大自由党黨員身份當選，後來才轉投魁人政團，外界曾因此質疑以魁人政團黨員身份競選的候選人能否當選国会议员<ref>{{Cite news|title = Gilles Duceppe: a pledge to sovereignty|url = http://www.cbc.ca/player/Digital+Archives/Politics/Federal+Politics/ID/1630387565/?page=6|accessdate = 26 May 2013|newspaper = Canadian Broadcasting Corporation Digital Archives|date = 23 September 1990|archive-date = 2015-02-21|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150221105131/http://www.cbc.ca/player/Digital+Archives/Politics/Federal+Politics/ID/1630387565/?page=6|dead-url = no}}</ref>。都賽佩的勝利顯示公開支持魁獨的魁人政團能夠獲取魁北克選民支持並贏取選舉。

都賽佩於1993年聯邦大選中以魁人政團黨員身份連任勞里埃－聖瑪莉選區国会议员，並獲任為該黨[[黨鞭|黨鞭]]<ref name="CE"/>；往後他從1997年至2008年皆在同一选区連任国会议员<ref name="LOP"/>。

== 魁北克集团领袖 ==
=== 1990年代末 ===
布沙爾（{{lang|fr|Lucien Bouchard}}）於1996年1月辭任魁人政團黨魁，改任魁北克省級政黨[[魁北克人党|魁北克人党]]黨魁，都賽佩則担任魁北克集团临时黨魁至戈捷（{{lang|fr|Michel Gauthier}}）於同年2月繼任為止。然而，戈捷因領導作風受黨員質疑而於1997年3月被逼辭職，都賽佩其後則成功當選黨魁。魁人政團當時為下議院第二大黨，都賽佩遂兼任[[加拿大官方反對黨領袖|下議院官方反對黨領袖]]<ref name="LOP"/><ref name="CE"/><ref name="gm61404"/>。

1997年聯邦大选競選期間，都賽佩身穿浴帽到访一家-{zh-cn:奶酪; zh-hk:芝士; zh-tw:起司}-工厂，成為加拿大媒体的笑柄<ref name="gm61404"/><ref>{{Cite news|title = Gilles Duceppe's hairnet raises eyebrows|url = http://www.cbc.ca/player/Digital+Archives/Politics/Federal+Politics/ID/1632288703/?page=4|accessdate = 26 May 2013|newspaper = Canadian Broadcasting Corporation Digital Archives|date = 9 June 1997|archive-date = 2015-09-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150924210252/http://www.cbc.ca/player/Digital+Archives/Politics/Federal+Politics/ID/1632288703/?page=4|dead-url = no}}</ref>。魁人政團在該屆大選贏取魁省75個下議院議席中的45個，失去[[官方反对党|官方反对党]]地位並滑落成第三大黨<ref name="CE"/>。該黨在2000年大选后的議席總數更降至38席<ref name="CE"/>，部分輿論遂批评都賽佩有欠競選能力，但他的黨魁地位并没有受到威胁<ref name="gm61404"/>。

=== 2000年代初 ===
[[保罗·马丁|保罗·马丁]]於2003年末接替[[让·克雷蒂安|让·克雷蒂安]]出任[[加拿大总理|总理]]和聯邦自由黨黨魁後不久，涉及該黨的赞助丑闻曝光，惠及魁北克集团。事緣[[1995年魁北克公民投票|1995年魁獨公投]]後，執政自由黨政府計劃在魁北克展開宣傳攻勢，宣揚聯邦政府對魁北克工業和其他範疇的貢獻，以抗衡魁人黨省政府的魁獨主張。然而該項計劃其後被揭發滥用和误用公帑，都賽佩就此强烈批评自由党。在[[2004年加拿大國會下議院選舉|2004年聯邦大選]]競選辩论中，都賽佩一方面清晰講解魁人政團的政策立場，另一方面則批評其他聯邦政黨黨魁許下的競選承諾，獲加拿大英法雙語媒体評为该届大选中辩论表現最好的黨魁。魁人政團在該屆大選赢得54个席位，几乎与1993年大選相等，而馬田領導的自由黨則只能保著少數執政地位<ref name="CE"/>。

克雷蒂安離任後，都賽佩成为加拿大眾主要政党中在任最久的黨魁。他作為魁人政團黨魁的近期表現獲得好評，惹來外界猜測他會否競逐省級[[魁北克人黨|魁北克人黨]]的党魁職位；該等传言在朗德里（{{lang|fr|Bernard Landry}}）於2005年6月4日辞任該黨黨魁后更趨踴躍。然而，都賽佩於同年6月13日表示無意竞逐魁北克人党党魁一职<ref>{{Cite news|title = CBC News Indepth: Parti Quebecois Timeline|url = http://www.cbc.ca/news/background/parti_quebecois/|accessdate = 26 May 2013|newspaper = Canadian Broadcasting Corporation|date = 16 November 2005|archive-date = 2012-11-11|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121111164428/http://www.cbc.ca/news/background/parti_quebecois/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

贊助醜聞調查報告公開後，由都賽佩領導的魁人政團、[[史蒂芬·哈珀|哈珀]]領導的[[加拿大保守黨|保守黨]]和[[傑克·林頓|林頓]]領導的[[加拿大新民主黨|新民主黨]]於2005年11月28日合作通過對自由黨少數政府提出的[[不信任動議|不信任動議]]，觸發另一場聯邦大選。魁北克集团黨內要員以至魁獨支持者皆普遍认为都賽佩的個人聲望，加上聯邦自由党在魁北克的民望低落，將有利魁人政團在魁北克贏取多數選票。多名魁獨支持者並寄望魁人政團若在聯邦大選表現理想的話，可让魁北克独立运动再次推向高潮，並為短期内再度舉行独立公投建立基礎。然而，保守黨和留加派的支持度在2006年聯邦大選競選期末段上升，魁北克集团因此仅贏取51个国会议员席位以及43%的整体选票<ref>{{Cite news|title = Conservatives make breakthrough in Quebec; Bloc wins 51 seats|url = http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/conservatives-make-breakthrough-in-quebec-bloc-wins-51-seats-1.586146|accessdate = 16 April 2014|newspaper = Canadian Broadcasting Corporation|date = 24 January 2006|archive-date = 2014-04-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140416201625/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/conservatives-make-breakthrough-in-quebec-bloc-wins-51-seats-1.586146|dead-url = no}}</ref>。保守黨在魁北克和安大略的議席數目皆有進帳，足以讓該黨取代自由黨，以少數地位上台執政。魁北克集团未有取得進一步突破，令魁北克民眾對魁獨運動的支持成疑。

=== 2000年代末 ===
[[File:Gilles_Duceppe1.jpg|left]]

在2007年3月的魁北克省选中，魁北克人党意外在[[魁北克国民议会|魁北克国民议会]]中淪為第三大黨，在[[魁北克自由党|魁北克自由党]]和[[魁北克民主行动党|魁北克民主行动党]]之后，布瓦克萊爾（{{lang|fr|André Boisclair}}）遂於同年5月8日辞任魁北克人党党魁。都賽佩在同年5月11日宣布有意競逐該党党魁<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/montreal/duceppe-marois-will-run-for-the-pq-s-top-spot-1.675574|title = Duceppe, Marois will run for the PQ's top spot|publisher = CBC News|date = 11 May 2007|accessdate = 16 April 2014|archive-date = 2019-08-13|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190813204946/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/montreal/duceppe-marois-will-run-for-the-pq-s-top-spot-1.675574|dead-url = no}}</ref>，卻於次日宣布退选<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/story/2007/05/12/duceppe-pq.html|title = Duceppe drops out of PQ race|publisher = CBC News|date = 2007-05-12|accessdate = 2012-02-20|archive-date = 2013-03-15|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130315002030/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/story/2007/05/12/duceppe-pq.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>，並宣布改為支持[[寶琳·馬華|寶琳·馬華]]<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://lcn.canoe.com/lcn/infos/national/archives/2007/05/20070512-174804.html|title = Gilles Duceppe se retire|publisher = Lcn.canoe.com|date = 2009-04-23|accessdate = 2010-01-31|archive-date = 2007-07-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070706181310/http://lcn.canoe.com/lcn/infos/national/archives/2007/05/20070512-174804.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

都賽佩等人認為聯邦政府和各省政府之間的財政失衡，都賽佩就此向總理哈珀施壓<ref name="CE"/>。此外，他亦要求哈珀承認魁北克為一個民族，並強烈反對聯邦政府削減對魁省提供的文化項目撥款<ref name="CE"/>。[[2008年加拿大國會下議院選舉|2008年聯邦大選]]競選期間，都賽佩以魁北克就文化、經濟和懲教事務自決為魁北克集团的政綱重點<ref name="CE"/>。該黨最終赢取国会49个席位，比大选前的48席多一个<ref>{{Cite news|title = Harper 'very pleased' with stronger minority|url = http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/story/2008/10/15/elexn-wednesday.html|accessdate = 26 May 2013|newspaper = Canadian Broadcasting Corporation|date = 15 October 2008}}</ref>，然而得票率仅達38%，为1997年来最低。

選後保守黨少數政府提出一系列具爭議性的經濟措施，促使自由黨、新民主黨和魁人政團商討推翻保守黨，並籌組[[聯合政府|聯合政府]]。都賽佩與另外兩黨黨魁於2008年12月1日簽署協議，向保守黨少數政府提出不信任動議，此後由自由黨和新民主黨組織聯合政府，魁人政團則[[信任供給|供給信任]]<ref name="CE"/>。然而，總理哈珀於同月4日向時任[[加拿大總督|總督]][[莊美楷|莊美楷]]提請將國會休會至2009年1月26日<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/canada/story/2008/12/04/harper-jean.html|title=GG agrees to suspend Parliament: Harper|publisher=[[加拿大廣播公司|CBC]]|date=2008-12-04|accessdate=2008-12-04|archive-date=2008-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081205134535/http://www.cbc.ca/canada/story/2008/12/04/harper-jean.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而自由黨此後則選出新黨魁並改為支持保守黨少數政府的財政預算案，聯合政府遂沒成事。縱雖如此，魁人政團和新民主黨仍繼續投票否決保守黨政府的議案<ref name="CE"/>。

=== 2010年代初 ===
[[File:Duceppe_Limoilou_15042011-4.JPG|right]]競選期間，都賽佩与一名选民交谈]]

2011年，國會委員會裁定哈珀政府蔑視國會<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www2.parl.gc.ca/content/hoc/Committee/403/PROC/Reports/RP5047570/procrp27/procrp27-e.pdf |title=Question of Privilege Relating to the Failure of the Government To Fully Provide the Documents as Ordered by the House: Report of the Standing Committee on Procedure and House Affairs |accessdate=April 26, 2011 |date=March 2011}}</ref>，自由黨因此向哈珀政府提出不信任動議<ref>{{cite news |author=Stephanie Levitz and Martin O'Hanlon, The Canadian Press: |url=http://www.globaltvcalgary.com/personalities/Liberals+introduce+confidence+motion/4489986/story.html |title=Harper government set to fall Friday, setting stage for vote in early May |publisher=Globaltvcalgary.com |date=March 23, 2011 |accessdate=April 13, 2011 |archive-date=2019-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822083926/https://globalnews.ca/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在自由黨、新民主黨和魁人政團合作下，下議院於3月25日以156票對145票通過動議<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/story/2011/03/25/pol-defeat.html |title=MPs gather for historic vote |author=CBC News |publisher=CBC |date=March 25, 2011 |accessdate=March 25, 2011 |archive-date=2011-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110328021055/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/story/2011/03/25/pol-defeat.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Mayeda|first=Andrew|title=Harper government falls|url=http://www.vancouversun.com/Harper+government+falls/4503131/story.html|accessdate=March 25, 2011|newspaper=Vancouver Sun|date=March 25, 2011}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，哈珀領導的少數政府因而倒台並觸發聯邦大選。

[[2011年加拿大國會下議院選舉|2011年聯邦大選]]競選期間，新民主黨黨魁[[傑克·林頓|林頓]]在各場黨魁電視辯論中表現理想，而他於4月3日現身[[加拿大廣播公司|加拿大廣播公司]][[加拿大法語頻道|法語電視頻道]]清談節目以口語化的[[魁北克法語|魁北克法語]]交談，大受魁北克省法語選民歡迎<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/layton-remains-game-despite-polls-showing-hes-the-odd-man-out/article575778/ |title=Three leaders, three accents |first=Lysiane |last=Gagnon |date=April 18, 2011 |accessdate=March 12, 2014 |publisher=The Globe and Mail |archive-date=2020-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129080502/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/layton-remains-game-despite-polls-showing-hes-the-odd-man-out/article575778/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外該黨的左傾政策立場也獲魁省民眾受落，該黨在魁省的支持度因此超越魁人政團<ref>{{cite news|author=Joanna Smith Ottawa Bureau|url=http://www.thestar.com/news/canada/politics/article/976225|title=NDP moves into tie with Liberals: Poll|publisher=thestar.com|date=April 13, 2011|accessdate=April 18, 2011|location=Toronto|archive-date=2012-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024031522/http://www.thestar.com/news/canada/politics/article/976225|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/18/canada-politics-idUSN1822211320110418|title=Canada's NDP pushes for bigger place in election sun|publisher=Reuters|date=February 14, 2011|accessdate=April 18, 2011|first=Randall|last=Palmer|archive-date=2015-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017001756/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/18/canada-politics-idUSN1822211320110418|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/canadavotes2011/story/2011/04/18/cv-election-layton-quebec-812.html|title=Layton sees growing Quebec support, targets Liberals|publisher=Cbc.ca|date=April 18, 2011|accessdate=April 18, 2011|archive-date=2013-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130417162852/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/canadavotes2011/story/2011/04/18/cv-election-layton-quebec-812.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。魁人政團在該屆大選慘敗，失去了43个席位，當中大部分自1993年大選以来便为該黨所盤據，都賽佩本人亦於自己的勞里埃－聖瑪莉選區敗予新民主党候選人拉弗迪耶（{{lang|fr|Hélène Laverdière}}）。为对魁人政團选举失败負责，都賽佩宣布辞任党魁，但承諾魁北克立国前將不会歇息<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://m.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/duceppe-resigns-as-bloc-leader-after-losing-riding/article2007598/?service=mobile|title = Duceppe resigns as Bloc leader after losing riding|publisher = The Globe and Mail|date = 24 August 2012|accessdate = 26 May 2013|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150218045937/http://m.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/duceppe-resigns-as-bloc-leader-after-losing-riding/article2007598/?service=mobile|archive-date = 2015-02-18|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

2012年1月，都賽佩被控在七年时间内，動用國會议员办公室的资金來支付魁北克集团的费用。他於同年2月在下議院内部经济审查组作供，否認自己有犯錯<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/ex-bloc-leader-s-testimony-raises-more-questions-1.1272890|title=Ex-Bloc leader's testimony raises more questions|publisher=CBC News|accessdate=4 June 2018|date=13 February 2012|archive-date=2016-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160315033441/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/ex-bloc-leader-s-testimony-raises-more-questions-1.1272890|dead-url=no}}</ref>。审查组於同年11月裁定都賽佩誤用該筆資金，但事情发生时相關附例尚未修改，故不能处罚都賽佩<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/commons-board-finds-ex-bq-leader-duceppe-misused-house-funds-1.1163136|title=Commons board finds ex-BQ leader Duceppe misused House funds|publisher=CBC News|accessdate=4 June 2018|date=27 November 2012|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205000227/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/commons-board-finds-ex-bq-leader-duceppe-misused-house-funds-1.1163136|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 離開政壇、短暫復出 ==
都賽佩在大選失败后成為一名政治分析員<ref name="dev">{{Cite news|title = Duceppe croit que le chef du Bloc devrait rectifier certains de ses propos|url = http://www.ledevoir.com/politique/canada/416897/duceppe-croit-que-le-chef-du-bloc-devrait-rectifier-certains-de-ses-propos|accessdate = August 27, 2014|date = August 26, 2014|archive-date = 2019-10-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191016124525/https://www.ledevoir.com/politique/canada/416897/duceppe-croit-que-le-chef-du-bloc-devrait-rectifier-certains-de-ses-propos|dead-url = no}}</ref>。魁北克集团在往後年間民望繼續低沉，並面臨内部分裂。[[加拿大廣播公司|加拿大廣播公司]]報道指該黨黨魁博略（{{lang|fr|Mario Beaulieu}}）曾獲民調公司告知，魁北克集团在他領導下無望在魁北克突破20%得票率，但在都賽佩領導下則有機贏取接近30%選票<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/gilles-duceppe-preparing-comeback-as-leader-of-bloc-qu%C3%A9b%C3%A9cois-1.3105751|title=Gilles Duceppe preparing comeback as leader of Bloc Québécois|first=Janyce|last=McGregor|publisher=CBC News|date=2015-06-09|accessdate=2020-04-19|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108133431/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/gilles-duceppe-preparing-comeback-as-leader-of-bloc-qu%c3%a9b%c3%a9cois-1.3105751|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該黨遂於2015年6月宣布博略辭任黨魁但留任黨主席，而都賽佩則重回党魁之位<ref name=back>{{cite news|title=Gilles Duceppe returns to lead Bloc Quebecois|url=http://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/gilles-duceppe-returns-to-lead-bloc-quebecois-1.2415002?hootPostID=062f4530d523c353466cfe09a9478b52|accessdate=June 10, 2015|work=CTV News|date=June 10, 2015|archive-date=2015-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610222826/http://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/gilles-duceppe-returns-to-lead-bloc-quebecois-1.2415002?hootPostID=062f4530d523c353466cfe09a9478b52|dead-url=no}}</ref>。為進行上述變動，魁北克集团党派高层同意將黨魁和黨主席分開成兩個職位<ref>{{cite news|title=Gilles Duceppe announces return to Bloc Québécois leadership|work=CBC News|date=June 10, 2015}}</ref>，並於7月1日生效<ref name=rat>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbc.ca/m/news/canada/montreal/gilles-duceppe-officially-named-leader-of-bloc-qu%C3%A9b%C3%A9cois-1.3135046|title=On Canada Day, Duceppe officially takes over Bloc Québécois|publisher=CBC News|accessdate=2015-10-25|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924144719/http://www.cbc.ca/m/news/canada/montreal/gilles-duceppe-officially-named-leader-of-bloc-qu%C3%A9b%C3%A9cois-1.3135046|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=rat2>{{cite news|title=Returning Bloc leader Gilles Duceppe targets NDP for fall election|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/gilles-duceppe-returns-to-lead-bloc-quebecois/article24893180/|accessdate=June 10, 2015|work=Globe and Mail|date=June 10, 2015|archive-date=2015-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121071123/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/gilles-duceppe-returns-to-lead-bloc-quebecois/article24893180/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

都賽佩於2015年8月2日宣布重回勞里埃－聖瑪莉選區競逐国会大选<ref name="DuceppeLaurier">{{Cite news|url = http://www.ledevoir.com/politique/quebec/446555/gilles-duceppe-devrait-se-presenter-dans-laurier-sainte-marie|title = Gilles Duceppe devrait se présenter dans Laurier Sainte-Marie|publisher = Le Devoir|date = August 1, 2015|accessdate = August 2, 2015|archive-date = 2020-11-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201108131457/https://www.ledevoir.com/politique/quebec/446555/gilles-duceppe-devrait-se-presenter-dans-laurier-sainte-marie|dead-url = no}}</ref>。在他領導下，魁人政團在[[2015年加拿大國會下議院選舉|該屆聯邦大選]]赢得10个席位，表現較上屆大選有所改善，但都賽佩本人仍未能成功當选重返國會，遂再次宣布辞职<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/montreal/canada-election-2015-bloc-quebecois-1.3278861|title=Bloc makes gains, but Gilles Duceppe loses his riding|publisher=CBC News|access-date=2015-10-25|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225090845/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/montreal/canada-election-2015-bloc-quebecois-1.3278861|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 個人生活 ==
都賽佩於1978年與約蘭德·布魯内爾（{{lang|fr|Yolande Brunelle}}）結婚，兩人育有兩名子女<ref name="autogenerated1"/>，當中阿歷西斯（{{lang|fr|Alexis Brunelle-Duceppe}}）於[[2019年加拿大聯邦大選|2019年聯邦大選]]中代表魁人政團首次當選魁省聖讓湖選區（{{lang|fr|Lac-Saint-Jean}}）國會下議院議員<ref name="LOP"/><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/alexis-brunelle-duceppe-different-style-1.5339749|title=Rookie MP Alexis Brunelle-Duceppe feeling 'pressure' of living up to his dad's example|work=The Canadian Press|publisher=CBC News|date=2019-10-29|accessdate=2020-04-19|archive-date=2019-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191031132742/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/alexis-brunelle-duceppe-different-style-1.5339749|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

